high_descs: turn around and walk to the stove at the end of the room, then hang a right and move over to the kitchen counter at the end of the room
grab the butter knife off of the kitchen counter
look up, then turn left and walk over to the black table on the right at the end of the counter
slice up the potato on the black table
turn right and walk back over to the kitchen counter on the left, it's not that far
place the knife down on the kitchen counter there
move left a bit to face the black table once again
grab a potato slice off of the black table there
turn around, then turn left again, and head down towards the end of the room, stop just short of the black fridge on your left, and turn to face it
place the potato slice inside of the fridge to cool, close the door naturally, then open it back up once it has cooled and pick that potato slice back up
turn left and walk to the end of the room so you can turn right and face the black table once again
place the potato slice down on the black table
anns.task_desc: place a cooled potato slice down on the black table

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the stove, and turn right towards the counter on the opposite side of the room.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the black table.
Slice the potato on the table into several pieces.
Take a step to the right to face the counter.
Place the knife to the left of the black cup on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the black table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn right and head towards the fridge on your left.
Place the potato next to the cup in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn left and head towards the black table at the right corner.
Place the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice potato on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around then head towards the white counter on your right.
Take the knife from the white counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the square black table on your right.
Slice the potato on the table in front of you.
Turn right then face the counter by the sink on your left.
Place the knife on the counter by the sink in front of you.
Turn left then face the black table on your right.
Take a potato slice from the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the potato slice in the fridge, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn left and face the black table to your right.
Place the potato slice on the black table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold potato slice on a black square table.

high_descs: Turn left slightly more than 90 degrees and go to the counter to the left of the sink, which is left of the fridge.
Pick up the knife from off of the counter, that is near the edge just to the right of the black table.
Move slightly left to face the black table.
Slice half of the potato that is at the back of the table, just left of the black glass.
Move slightly right to face the counter next to the sink.
Place the knife on the counter just to the left of the black glass.
Move slightly left to face the black table.
Pick up one slice of potato that is next to the black glass.
Turn right and walk past the sink to the fridge.  Face the fridge.

Open the bottom door of the fridge, put the potato slice on the middle shelf to the left of the white cup, and close the door.  Wait a few seconds, then open the door, take out the potato slice, and shut the door.
Turn left and walk past the sink to the black table.  Face the black table.
Put the potato slice on the front right corner of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put one chilled potato slice onto a black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Walk to the black table on your left.
Cut up the potato on the black table.
Walk to the counter on your right.
Place the knife to the left of the black vase on the counter.
Walk to the black table on your left.
Pick up a piece of potato from the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the piece of potato in the fridge and then pick the piece of potato up.
Turn left and walk to the small black table to the left of the sink.
Place the piece of potato on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled piece of potato onto the black table to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, turn left and walk to the counter with a knife.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Go to a lower black table to the left.
Slice a potato in the back behind the cabbage and spatula.
Turn right and go to the white counter.
Set the knife on the counter next to the glass.
Go back to the sliced potato.
Pick up a slice from the potato.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the potato slice in. Open the refrigerator again and take the slice out.
Turn left and carry the potato slice back to the small black table.
Set the potato slice on the right front corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled slice of potato on a table.
